  "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\nWe should provide a full-featured interface to EpochContext.\r\nIt's nice to have a consistent interface for interacting with EpochContext.\r\n\r\nWe could add some useful methods to EpochContext, which may lead to more readable code, better devex.\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\nAdd convenience methods `getAttestingIndices` and `getCommitteeAssignment` to `EpochContext`.\r\nConsider adding state transition methods to `EpochContext`. Eg: `processSlots`, `stateTransition`.\r\nUse in place of lower level functions, where applicable.\r\n\r\n**Describe alternatives you've considered**\r\nLeave as is.\r\n\r\n**Additional context**\r\nSee https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/pull/1131#discussion_r453713607",
